events.text:
Thanks for helping us clear out the way for our customers. But we still need supplies from the capitol to fulfill our orders down here.
Take this, it's an invoice for a fellow named Jameson down west in Strahmholde where the trade district is at.
He has our shipment of goods that we need.
Any word from Jameson about our shipment?
Wonderful! I should be able to complete all of our orders in time thanks to you. To show my appreciation, I would like to offer some monetary compensation for your troubles.
Hello, what's this? Oh, it's the order for those two brothers. Let me just package that up for you. Here you go, ready for delivery.
